Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:27.06,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you wake up after finding something tasty to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:28.04,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I was dreaming of Yoitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:30.04,m,,0000,0000,0000,,My hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.80,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I tell you how I truly feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:40.51,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:42.51,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:47.51,m,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H575F66&\4c&H575F66&\pos(320,336)\blur3}Wolf and the Sudden Crack
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:54.59,m,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:56.91,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and put it back under the blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:01.80,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat my tail like a hand warmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:07.74,m,,0000,0000,0000,,With fur as fine as that, I couldn't match it even if I had a pile of top-grade pelts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:16.47,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:18.46,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a present in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:29.06,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Our next stop, Kumerson, is owned by the Furoania nobles, and there are a lot of heathens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:32.29,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Religious symbols are banned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:36.57,m,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an unspoken rule that even nuns and monks follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:38.79,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything works out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:40.63,m,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:42.17,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You really though I had a present for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:44.51,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate my ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:47.08,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I was expecting more of a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:51.33,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.58,m,,0000,0000,0000,,This is payback!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:54.69,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:55.93,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:05.97,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we still not at Kumerson?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:08.03,m,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll arrive today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:09.87,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, not long now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.23,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Not long, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:18.23,m,,0000,0000,0000,,So the next meal I'll be freed from hard bitter rye wheat bread and gruel made from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.13,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:22.59,m,,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that Kumerson is in the middle of a big town-wide festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:26.24,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there will be all sorts of food, so look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:28.13,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:30.92,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Will your pocket be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:38.18,m,,0000,0000,0000,,There's enough to buy you food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:43.26,m,,0000,0000,0000,,But won't the inn be shabby because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:46.15,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to stay somewhere decent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:51.06,m,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you aren't going to insist we each have our own fireplace or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.91,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't plan to be that picky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:57.58,m,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want you to use buying food as an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:04:58.17,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:05:01.57,m,,0000,0000,0000,,"We don't have enough money so we have to share one bed" or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:11.55,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear that from someone who snores so noisily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:15.89,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't snore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:18.96,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you're not even my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:23.21,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ears can tell I'm not lying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:31.78,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:34.73,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, you like me this way don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:37.73,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Foolish men prefer weaker women right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:41.25,m,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were the weak princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:44.00,m,,0000,0000,0000,,then you'd have to be the mighty knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:47.34,m,,0000,0000,0000,,But what is it in reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:50.34,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you did act the knight once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:51.05,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:52.48,m,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you've forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:53.99,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:58.22,m,,0000,0000,0000,,when we got caught up in the silver coins affair, in the sewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:00.85,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:04.15,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a knight isn't just about physical power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:10.59,m,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the first time anyone had protected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:17.14,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:20.15,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll also treat me well from now on, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:24.90,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.04,m,,0000,0000,0000,,about what I said earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:32.14,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I like that part of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.39,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:36.29,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't mind if the room only has one bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.29,m,,0000,0000,0000,,but then there has to be two meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:42.93,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:07:01.40,m,,0000,0000,0000,,There's good fish in that crowded place over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:05.40,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we buy some first-rate fish and have it cooked for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.65,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Some fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:10.78,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, could you sell me a few?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.59,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:16.66,m,,0000,0000,0000,,All my fish have already been bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:20.52,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon my rudeness, but might you be a traveling merchant?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:23.06,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I just came from Rubinhaigen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:27.05,m,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, if you follow that path for half a day, you'll reach a lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:30.67,m,,0000,0000,0000,,The carp today is very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:34.59,m,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get a good deal you'll be able to acquire a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:35.82,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:37.72,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just looking for a few for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:45.16,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you've come up with a new business idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:49.25,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that was embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:51.84,m,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for fish for dinner tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:54.05,m,,0000,0000,0000,,does that mean you're staying in Kumerson tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:54.66,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:57.35,m,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here for the grand winter fair and the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:07:59.56,m,,0000,0000,0000,,The Radora festival is very popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:02.16,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you already booked an inn to stay at?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:04.52,m,,0000,0000,0000,,The festival starts the day after tomorrow right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:06.94,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me everywhere's already fully booked?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:08.30,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:12.15,m,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case I'll try asking the trading firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:13.74,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You belong to a guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:15.82,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, but which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:19.43,m,,0000,0000,0000,,The Rowen Trading Guild firm in Kumerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:21.54,m,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:23.19,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I also belong to the Rowen Trading Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:25.44,m,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be God's guidance—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.16,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying that is taboo in this area, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:29.92,m,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:32.69,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also a believer from the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:36.18,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Fermi Amati.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:39.01,m,,0000,0000,0000,,For business, I go by Amati.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:40.68,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Craft Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:43.06,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise, I go by Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:44.71,m,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my traveling companion, Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:48.71,m,,0000,0000,0000,,We're journeying together for various reasons, but we're not married.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:58.93,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.93,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.25,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Horo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:05.69,m,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a nun on a pilgrimage, 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.19,m,,0000,0000,0000,,basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:12.82,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose problems in life are God's way of testing us,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:17.04,m,,0000,0000,0000,,as arranging for two rooms will be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:18.70,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:23.89,m,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ask my business acquaintances to help out, they should be able to spare a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:24.70,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:25.74,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:29.95,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to enjoy plenty of good fish at trading partner's inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.95,0:09:32.74,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You look young but you have good business sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:34.05,m,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave it in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.41,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll arrange it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:43.18,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:56.86,m,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice spacious room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:09:59.35,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate you introducing us to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:02.67,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.49,m,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:08.75,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad we met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:10.43,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:11.63,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:16.17,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a really pretty and wonderful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:22.09,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too different from how you were earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:24.15,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I just know how to act in different situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:26.10,m,,0000,0000,0000,,The wine and fish here are truly delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:29.31,m,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid has quite good senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:31.86,m,,0000,0000,0000,,While being so young, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:34.94,m,,0000,0000,0000,,The amount he was dealing in was above average too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:37.82,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to that, the stuff you were selling...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.24,m,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:40.87,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:42.49,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I know they were nails!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:46.24,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean you should deal in more interesting goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:49.75,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you hit that bad from failing in Rubinhaigen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:53.72,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Well it is plain, but it should yield relatively good profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:56.76,m,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm not just carrying boring things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:01.38,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on the wagon too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:07.47,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:11.63,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You ordered another just a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:13.73,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I guess that's about all you can handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:18.56,m,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't hurt to be a little nicer to me, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:21.67,m,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're nice to men, they get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:25.74,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand you expecting me to fall for the same flattery each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:27.74,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, from now on I'll ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:28.62,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.56,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Men should be kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:35.50,m,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I act upset,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:37.90,m,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll want to be kind to me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.89,m,,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite a pale wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:48.14,m,,0000,0000,0000,,It called 'burning wine'.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:50.32,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you drink that much at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:52.76,m,,0000,0000,0000,,See, what did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:54.41,m,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nostalgic flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:00.61,m,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the wine in Yoitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.54,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to drink it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:05.60,m,,0000,0000,0000,,How nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:07.24,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how everyone's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:10.07,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to arriving at Yoitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:18.03,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:22.61,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:26.84,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoitsu's wine is the best after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.69,m,,0000,0000,0000,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:36.56,m,,0000,0000,0000,,what happened to that Yoitsu village?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:56.93,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I see this face a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:03.17,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought you some water and a bucket, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:07.06,m,,0000,0000,0000,,And about Radona festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:13.27,m,,0000,0000,0000,,The real events start tomorrow, so there's no need to be anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:16.91,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sleep there quietly for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:23.03,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off to see a business associate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:48.64,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:55.31,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Ré su pan dia milto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:56.73,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Vant derji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.43,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Piréji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:00.21,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Bao.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:01.19,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Bao.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:04.85,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Bao.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:08.74,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I interrupting some business?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:09.32,m,,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:13.83,m,,0000,0000,0000,,he was just regaling me with tales of the god of Pitora mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:15.47,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:18.20,m,,0000,0000,0000,,There's merit in being able to communicate using foreign languages.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:22.71,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I didn't go around talking everyone into deals, Adelle would scold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.02,m,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:27.09,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You came here to talk business, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:28.79,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:30.72,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought nails from Rubinhaigen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:31.71,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Nails?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:34.10,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is a wheat store you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:37.19,m,,0000,0000,0000,,But you get a lot of customers from the north right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:40.85,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Nails are required goods to last through the long winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:43.83,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there is a demand for them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:45.19,m,,0000,0000,0000,,How many?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:47.57,m,,0000,0000,0000,,120 three-pattes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:50.20,m,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Note: "pattes" are some form of measurement
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:50.20,m,,0000,0000,0000,,200 four-pattes, 200 five-pattes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:54.31,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a letter of gauranteed quality from the Rubinhaigen Blacksmith's guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.20,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take them for 10½ rumiones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.11,m,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:02.96,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you heard about the crash in battle equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:06.87,m,,0000,0000,0000,,The Northern military expedition was canceled this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.87,0:15:10.56,m,,0000,0000,0000,,so swords and armor are being sold dirt cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:12.97,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that the market for nails has fallen too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:15.82,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Even 10 rumiones might be too expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:19.06,m,,0000,0000,0000,,That's only true for the southern regions, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:22.19,m,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that raw materials availability has increased,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:27.50,m,,0000,0000,0000,,but melting metal into nails during the winter season would drive up the prices of firewood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:30.85,m,,0000,0000,0000,,No one would be willing to incur the wrath of the townsfolk in doing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.85,0:15:33.23,m,,0000,0000,0000,,so the price of nails shouldn't be affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:39.09,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:42.23,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you not have gone elsewhere to sell nails?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:44.43,m,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were wheat, I could find ways to bargain,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:46.09,m,,0000,0000,0000,,but nails are outside my field.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.42,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about 16 rumiones?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:49.68,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Too expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:50.76,m,,0000,0000,0000,,13 rumiones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:51.98,m,,0000,0000,0000,,15.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:55.64,m,,0000,0000,0000,,14 and two thirds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:15:58.70,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.81,m,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.14,m,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.73,m,,0000,0000,0000,,So, payment in cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.18,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you want credit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:06.72,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Credit please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:07.69,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Appeciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:09.90,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's charging cash this time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.56,m,,0000,0000,0000,,The scarcity of cash makes it difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:13.24,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Lanto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.57,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:16.92,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You have an apprentice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:19.07,m,,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural when you set up a store.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:22.88,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Load all these boxes onto my cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:24.83,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be selling them at Hans' later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:27.76,m,,0000,0000,0000,,That ironsmith person?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:29.89,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go move them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:31.35,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:34.22,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be here until the end of the festival right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:36.73,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over at least once for a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:38.32,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll introduce you to Adelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:42.45,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:43.49,m,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:45.23,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you taken in by my store's beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:47.08,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:49.23,m,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good store.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:50.93,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:53.74,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Young people like you have much better ahead of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:57.99,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You're close to opening an even bigger store, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:02.37,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:09.14,m,,0000,0000,0000,,The festival is only a day away now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:11.50,m,,0000,0000,0000,,So we've got pre-festival celebration to do tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:14.29,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just using it as an excuse to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:17.93,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:22.86,m,,0000,0000,0000,,If it'd been anyone less serious but brainless, I'm sure they wouldn't have put up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:24.04,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:29.40,m,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like a long time ago since we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:32.40,m,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:36.87,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, you were much more embarrassed at my temptations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:38.03,m,,0000,0000,0000,,It was cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:41.65,m,,0000,0000,0000,,And you only drank half as much as you do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.65,0:17:44.61,m,,0000,0000,0000,,And you wouldn't have answered back like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:48.72,m,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange, isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:51.42,m,,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:56.42,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally it'd be much easier to get by in wolf form.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:58.93,m,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easier to chew meat,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:04.43,m,,0000,0000,0000,,and I still can't get used to these cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:06.69,m,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:14.31,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll be okay for a while like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:17.00,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You let down your guard when drinking in that form too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:19.78,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:21.03,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.03,m,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a fool here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:23.78,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You damned...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:24.91,m,,0000,0000,0000,,fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:27.60,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:29.62,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:36.92,m,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there's something I want to ask before you pass out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:38.46,m,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:41.96,m,,0000,0000,0000,,About possible clues that could help us find your hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:43.43,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Clues?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:48.01,m,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a predetermined path ahead of us, and we don't have a useful map.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:51.74,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on the circumstances we might not be able to go straight there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:57.19,m,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, don't you remember the name of any nearby towns?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:07.39,m,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:08.54,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Niohira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.28,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Niohira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:10.46,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:13.21,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's famous for its hotsprings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:19.22,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's full of heathens, I heard there are a lot of archbishops and royalty there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:20.59,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:22.09,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Even these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:26.91,m,,0000,0000,0000,,The hotsprings were good for healing our wounds back then, so we went a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:30.56,m,,0000,0000,0000,,So if this way was North and Niohira was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:32.72,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Where would Yoitsu be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:35.05,m,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:36.56,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Southwest, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:38.96,m,,0000,0000,0000,,How far?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:42.06,m,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd take me two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:44.23,m,,0000,0000,0000,,For people it'd take...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:45.32,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:47.72,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Two days, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:51.37,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Two days at that speed would be quite a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:54.01,m,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd take me a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:56.10,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:58.96,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine as long as there's good food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.56,m,,0000,0000,0000,,There's too wide an area to cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:11.81,m,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't assume you took the roads as a wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:14.98,m,,0000,0000,0000,,If things don't go well it could take a year or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:18.55,m,,0000,0000,0000,,This wine is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:19.98,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:23.24,m,,0000,0000,0000,,If we got to Niohira, wouldn't you be able to go back alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:30.47,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:33.77,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'd be able to go back alone if we got to Niohira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:34.50,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:39.96,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Loneliness is a sickness that leads to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:41.60,m,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.68,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean that, we still have traveling to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:46.47,m,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.11,0:20:49.91,m,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll take me as far as Niohira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:52.98,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I still want to look around more towns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:54.47,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:56.84,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do all I can to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:00.66,m,,0000,0000,0000,,What I just said...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:03.24,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier I said men are measured by their kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:06.75,m,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:09.43,m,,0000,0000,0000,,too pampered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:12.75,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terrible, I'm always thinking in our scale of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:16.75,m,,0000,0000,0000,,The time you age is like the time it takes us to blink.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:20.75,m,,0000,0000,0000,,A year of that short lifespan is precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:25.55,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I just... forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:28.69,m,,0000,0000,0000,,That may be true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:31.19,m,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:34.27,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll feel bad if you make faces like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.28,0:21:37.30,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:40.59,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who didn't consider the obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.59,0:21:42.98,m,,0000,0000,0000,,It's comfortable being by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:43.78,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:46.78,m,,0000,0000,0000,,ended up depending on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:53.87,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems I'm drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:57.87,m,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better sleep soon, or who knows what I'll come up with next.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.41,0:23:52.91,m,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Wolf and the Calm Before the Storm.
